“Authority” has the meaning assigned to the word in the Act;
“benefit” means a financial, health or other advantage or profit
gained from research;
“biological material” has the meaning assigned to the words
in the Act;
“clinical trial” has the meaning assigned to the words in the
Act;
“material transfer agreement” has the meaning assigned to
the words in the Act; and
“standard operating procedure” means a written instruction
intended to document how to perform a routine activity.
